---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE_CONFIG } from '../config';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us - InSpotGO"
  description="Learn about InSpotGO's mission to help you discover the best tech products, software, and SaaS tools through honest, expert reviews."
>
  <div class="container content-page">
    <h1>About InSpotGO</h1>
    
    <div class="intro">
      <p class="lead">
        {SITE_CONFIG.slogan}
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        At InSpotGO, we believe that making informed purchasing decisions shouldn't be complicated. 
        With countless tech products, software solutions, and SaaS tools available today, finding 
        the right option for your needs can be overwhelming.
      </p>
      <p>
        That's why we exist. Our mission is to cut through the noise and provide honest, thorough, 
        and unbiased reviews that help you make confident decisions. Whether you're shopping for 
        the latest laptop, searching for productivity software, or evaluating SaaS tools for your 
        business, we've got you covered.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p>InSpotGO specializes in three core areas:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Tech Product Reviews:</strong> From laptops and smartphones to accessories and 
          smart home devices, we test and review the latest technology to help you find products 
          that match your needs and budget.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Software & SaaS Evaluations:</strong> We dive deep into software applications 
          and SaaS platforms, comparing features, pricing, and user experience to help you choose 
          the right tools for productivity, creativity, and business growth.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Buying Guides & Comparisons:</strong> Our comprehensive guides break down complex 
          decisions into simple recommendations, helping you understand what to look for and which 
          options offer the best value.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Our Review Process</h2>
      <p>
        Every review on InSpotGO follows a rigorous research and evaluation process:
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <strong>Research:</strong> We study product specifications, manufacturer claims, and 
          user feedback from multiple sources.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Testing:</strong> When possible, we test products hands-on to verify performance 
          and usability claims.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Comparison:</strong> We compare products against competitors to provide context 
          and identify the best options in each category.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Analysis:</strong> We evaluate pros, cons, and value to give you a complete picture.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Updates:</strong> We regularly update reviews to reflect new versions, price changes, 
          and emerging alternatives.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Our Values</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>üéØ Honesty</h3>
          <p>
            We provide transparent, unbiased reviews. If a product has flaws, we'll tell you. 
            We never let affiliate relationships influence our honest opinions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>üîç Thoroughness</h3>
          <p>
            We dig deep into features, performance, and value to give you the complete information 
            you need to make informed decisions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>üë• User-Focused</h3>
          <p>
            Your needs come first. We recommend products that genuinely solve problems and provide 
            value, not just those with the highest commissions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>üìö Expertise</h3>
          <p>
            Our team stays current with technology trends and industry developments to provide 
            informed, accurate recommendations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        InSpotGO is supported through affiliate partnerships. When you purchase products through 
        our links, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. This helps us maintain 
        the site and continue creating valuable content.
      </p>
      <p>
        However, our affiliate relationships never influence our editorial decisions. We only 
        recommend products we believe offer genuine value to our readers. For more details, 
        please read our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a> and 
        <a href="/editorial-policy">Editorial Policy</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        Have questions, suggestions, or feedback? We'd love to hear from you! 
        Visit our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> to get in touch.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can also reach us at: <a href="mailto:{SITE_CONFIG.contact.email}">{SITE_CONFIG.contact.email}</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .content-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .intro {
    margin: 2rem 0;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  section {
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }
  
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  ul, ol {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }
  
  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  
  .value-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  
  .value-card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .value-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
